data.description: Discover the pinnacle of contemporary luxury in this remarkable 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom Westin Home nestled in Waters Edge on Lake Houston. Upon entering, be captivated by the impressive rotunda and an abundance of natural light streaming in through the floor-to-ceiling windows. The chef's kitchen features a stylish island and a gas stove top. The primary suite boasts bay windows and a spa-inspired bathroom. With a full bath, the second bedroom on the first floor serves as an ideal space for guests or a mother-in-law suite. Upstairs, a spacious game room and three additional bedrooms await. Take advantage of community amenities such as an exercise facility, swimming pool, playgrounds, and serene pond-side walks. Convenient access to Beltway & 1960, shopping, and schools makes this the ideal forever home.
